Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子 交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 比之前進步了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害 貞子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 貞子剛剛不是在那嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.34,0:01:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.34,0:01:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬間移動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.29,0:01:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得不錯 貞子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.53,0:01:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來 沒準我們能在體育祭上拿到優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.23,0:01:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有白買那件紅色T恤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.98,0:01:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(415,65)\fs22}瞬間移動 瞬間移動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:01:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被表揚了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.12,0:19:35.42,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,banner;28;0;60,翻譯:キョン 瑤瑤　校譯:キョン　時間:キョン　後期:風一樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.96,0:01:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那些都是風早同學教給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.11,0:02:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳給風早同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好的傳到我這來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.82,0:02:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像剛才那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試一下停球回傳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別著急
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.63,0:02:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.03,0:03:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出了好多汗 火速換下衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子你先回教室好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都還沒回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.31,0:03:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人...法國...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 是胡桃同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:04:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個 男生們在為體育祭練習還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那怎麼辦好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很自然的就來和我說話了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得和風早同學很像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 你可能不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾有一次幫我撿過卷子 非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 那個是小事一樁嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼正式的被道謝 有點不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給人的感覺真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 好有女孩子的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直憧憬的理想少女就站在我的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的越看越覺得...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像人偶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 我怎麼把心裡想的話說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 是我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑沼爽子同學對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本名 話說 剛才的人偶說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撿卷子的事我也清楚地記著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那時候我就是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像人偶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像人偶 像人偶.....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡桃 再不去操場就要遲到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我一會兒再來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像頭髮會長長的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像人偶一樣 出生以來頭一次被人這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子 出什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼明顯的發著呆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 其實
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.57,0:06:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才很少見的被人表揚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我像人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子 爽子人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是表揚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 不算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們說不定能贏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能 絕對能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有些不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為沒穿毛衫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生的情況怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不壞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為什麼貞子進化了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才胡桃同學來找過風早同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事呢 大概是體育祭委員會的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 胡桃同學也是委員
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你見過胡桃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.93,0:07:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 和吉田同學分開後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:08:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 你又說吉田同學了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小千
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說我們不是也叫她貞子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.54,0:08:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中途改變稱呼還真不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就是說嘛 貞子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 本來也沒必要強行改變嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑沼爽子同學對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 如果下次有機會交談的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就直接叫名字試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小胡桃什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 龍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.61,0:08:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你記得貞子的全名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑山隆子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一點 龍 就差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 對於龍來說已經不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還挺自信的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.44,0:08:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是黑沼 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做個示範吧 風早
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 告訴龍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不錯不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下來直接叫名字看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓不習慣叫也不習慣被叫的爽子習慣一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了爽子的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽......
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼叫得出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜也是 只是開個玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好緊張啊 剛剛好緊張啊 心跳不止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 最近一直很緊張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得好像 比從前還緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是風早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他說話的女生是誰啊 好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你女友就在身旁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小胡桃可看不上你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看人家倆多配
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很般配
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想問風早借的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是CD啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞了 我忘了 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 之前明明告訴你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 明天給你帶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:11:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她當成榜樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我燙一下頭髮好不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飄飄的那種...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燙髮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 剛剛腦中突然掠過的恐怖畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 為什麼你一直是這個髮型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為長頭髮比較有女孩子的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比較喜歡有女孩子感覺的...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H131113&}(少女)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 不改變長度 換下顏色怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不錯 茶色 茶色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,染成茶色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶色...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得這樣存在感比較低嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再燙一下試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒吧女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 卷髮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的不良少女?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.87,0:13:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你還是這樣子最好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.08,0:13:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我們希望你一輩子都能保持這個髮型
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 飄飄醬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會帶著這個髮型度過我的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 你一直都是這個髮型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.54,0:13:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼突然想到要燙頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺飄飄的頭髮很可愛...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是想要變可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是為了讓別人說自己像人偶一樣漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說那樣會很高興 但自己還沒敢奢望那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥 放學後自主訓練?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足球的話 可以問小痞借啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.54,0:14:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡桃實在是太可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要變得可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始有了這樣的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然知道自己沒辦法變得向她那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會用自己的方式變得可愛...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:14:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平野同學 遠籐同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悅 小朋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒是要去自主訓練嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 小千和綾音去借足球了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在等她們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足球？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是荒井老師會借給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好滴 我借給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能得到優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.65,0:15:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管五個還是十個隨便你們拿 隨便拿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不了那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他們全滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過綾音是和小悅一起參加排球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:16:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說三個人一起練習起來比較方便
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以綾音也一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是三人一起比較好呢 貞子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體育祭加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是...朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是很久沒見了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是會有人主動和他說話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有人氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...風早沒一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因為要參加體育祭委員會嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委員會裡還有其他同一個初中的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:17:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直呼她的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起來 這或許是第一次聽到...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早同學直呼女生的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼叫得出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能那麼自然的叫出口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人的關係很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛的感覺是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然從來都沒有問過他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早同學的心裡有沒有一個特別的女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直呼她的名字算不算特別呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.58,0:17:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.23,0:17:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也練習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是看著風早同學的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口就會痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口就會痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.70,0:18:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.99,0:18:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被胡桃搭話之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是不是想要說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.81,0:19:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼呢 我也一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.05,0:19:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 做什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.76,0:19:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像對什麼都太過在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.27,0:19:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對風早同學太過在意了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子好多汗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛太緊張了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 都擦好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能已經開始崇拜她了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道什麼時候她們的關係就這麼好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 只是想和爽子說說話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇拜者和偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.99,0:20:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易成了朋友嘛 是吧 爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 崇拜
